 to forgive me for all the promises I made but then I broke them I ask You to forgive what I decided to do for the sake of Your Benevolent Face, but then my intentions were mixed with things that did not please You I ask You to forgive me for all the blessings that You bestowed on me but I used them to insist on doing acts of Your Disobedience I ask You to forgive every sin I committed, and every offense I made and every bad deed that I performed.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "يَا اِلٰهِيْ اَسْتَغْفِرُكَ مِمَّا تُبْتُ اِلَيْكَ مِنْهُ ثُمَّ عُدْتُ فِيْهِ وَاَسْتَغْفِرُكَ مِمَّا وَعَدْتُكَ مِنْ نَفْسِيْ ثُمَّ اَخْلَفْتُكَ فِيْهِ وَاَسْتَغْفِرُكَ مِمَّا اَرَدْتُ بِهٖ وَجْهَكَ الْكَرِيْمَ فَخَالَطَنِيْ مَا لَيْسَ لَكَ رِضًا وَاَسْتَغْفِرُكَ لِكُلِّ نِعْمَةٍ اَنْعَمْتَ بِهَا عَلَيَّ فَقَوِيْتُ بِهَا عَلٰى مَعَاصِيْكَ وَاَسْتَغْفِرُكَ لِكُلِّ ذَنْۢبٍ اَذْنَبْتُهٗ وَلِكُلِّ خَطِيْئَةٍ ارْتَكَبْتُهَا وَلِكُلِّ سُوْءٍ اَتَيْتُهٗ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, 